<p><strong> 测试平台配件简介</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200917/dd6cc64fd1f24452b00238044b18c4b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">CPU：i9-10900K</p>
